  fancyName: 
  nickname: mal
  version: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d0ec49142d5c7c24fb05ee739840cab0, type: 2}
  description: 
  chapters:
  - verses:
    - name: '1: An Oracle Against Edom'
      title: An Oracle Against Edom
      number: 1
      content: ' An oracle. The word of Yahweh to Israel through Malachi.  '
      comments: []
    - name: '2: '
      title: 
      number: 2
      content: "\u201CI have loved you,\u201D says Yahweh, but you say, \u201CHow
        have you loved us?\u201D&nbsp;\u201CIs Esau not Jacob\u2019s brother?\u201D
        declares Yahweh. \u201CI have loved Jacob, "
      comments: []
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: "but Esau I have hated. I have made his mountain ranges a desolation,
        and given his inheritance to the jackals of the desert.\u201D "
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: "If Edom says, \u201CWe are shattered, but we will return and rebuild
        the ruins,\u201D Yahweh of hosts says this: \u201CThey may build, but I will
        tear down; and they will be called a territory of wickedness, and the people
        with whom Yahweh is angry forever.\u201D "
      comments: []
    - name: '5: An Oracle Against the Temple Priesthood'
      title: An Oracle Against the Temple Priesthood
      number: 5
      content: "Your eyes will see this, and you will say, \u201CYahweh is great
        beyond the borders of Israel.\u201D "
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: "\u201CA son honors his father, and a slave his master; but if I am
        a father, where is my honor, and if I am a master, where is my reverence?\u201D
        says Yahweh of hosts to you, O priests, who despise my name. \u201CBut you
        say, \u2018How have we despised your name?\u2019 "
      comments: []
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: "You are presenting defiled food on my altar! But you ask, \u2018How
        have we defiled you?\u2019 By saying that the table of Yahweh is despised! "
      comments: []
    - name: '8: '
      title: 
      number: 8
      content: "When you offer a blind animal for sacrifice, is that not wrong? And
        when you offer the lame and the one who is ill, is that not wrong? Present
        it, please, to your governor! Will he be pleased with you? Will he show you
        favor?\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '9: '
      title: 
      number: 9
      content: "So then, implore the favor of God so that he will be gracious to
        us. \u201CThis is what you have done. Will he show favor to any of you?\u201D
        says Yahweh of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '10: '
      title: 
      number: 10
      content: "\u201CWho also among you will shut the temple doors so that you will
        not kindle fire in vain on my altar? I take no pleasure in you,\u201D says
        Yahweh of hosts, \u201Cand I will not accept an offering from your hand. "
      comments: []
    - name: '11: '
      title: 
      number: 11
      content: "From the rising of the sun to its setting, my name is great among
        the nations, and in every place incense is being presented to my name, and
        a pure offering. For my name is great among the nations,\u201D says Yahweh
        of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '12: '
      title: 
      number: 12
      content: "\u201CBut you are profaning it by saying the table of the Lord is
        defiled, and its fruit\u2014its food\u2014is despised! "
      comments: []
    - name: '13: '
      title: 
      number: 13
      content: "And you say, \u2018Look! This is a weariness,\u2019 and you sniff
        with disdain at it,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. \u201CAnd you bring the stolen,
        the lame, and the one that is sick\u2014this you bring as the offering! Should
        I accept it from your hand?\u201D says Yahweh. "
      comments: []
    - name: '14: '
      title: 
      number: 14
      content: "\u201CCursed is the one who cheats, who has in his flock a male and
        vows it, but instead sacrifices a blemished one to the Lord! For I am a great
        king,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts, \u201Cand my name is awesome among the
        nations.\u201D "
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - name: '1: '
      title: 
      number: 1
      content: " \u201CAnd so then, O priests, this command is for you: "
      comments: []
    - name: '2: '
      title: 
      number: 2
      content: "If you will not listen, and if you will not take it to heart to give
        glory to my name,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts, \u201Cthen I will send the
        curse on you, and I will curse your blessings; moreover I have already cursed
        them because you are not taking it to heart.  "
      comments: []
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: 'Look! I am going to rebuke your offspring, and I will scatter offal
        on your faces, the offal of your religious feasts, and you will be carried
        to it.  '
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: "\u201CThen you will know that I have sent to you this command, that
        my covenant with Levi continues,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '5: '
      title: 
      number: 5
      content: "\u201CMy covenant with him was one of life and peace, and I gave
        them to him. This required reverence, and he revered me and stood in awe
        before my name. "
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: 'The instruction of truth was in his mouth, and wickedness was not
        found on his lips. In peace and in uprightness he walked with me, and he
        brought back many from sin.  '
      comments: []
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: 'For the lips of the priest should guard knowledge, and they should
        seek instruction from his mouth, for he is the messenger of Yahweh of hosts. '
      comments: []
    - name: '8: '
      title: 
      number: 8
      content: "But you, you have turned from the way; you have caused many to stumble
        by your instruction; you have ruined the covenant of Levi,\u201D says Yahweh
        of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '9: Yahweh Hates Faithlessness'
      title: Yahweh Hates Faithlessness
      number: 9
      content: "\u201CAnd in turn I have made you despised and humbled before all
        the people, inasmuch as you are not keeping my way, but are favoring your
        own instruction.\u201D  "
      comments: []
    - name: '10: '
      title: 
      number: 10
      content: 'Do we not all have one father? Has not one God created us? Why then
        are we unfaithful to one another, profaning the covenant of our ancestors?  '
      comments: []
    - name: '11: '
      title: 
      number: 11
      content: 'Judah has been faithless, and a detestable thing has been done in
        Israel and in Jerusalem. Judah has profaned the sanctuary of Yahweh which
        he loves, and has married the daughter of a foreign god. '
      comments: []
    - name: '12: '
      title: 
      number: 12
      content: 'May Yahweh cut off from the tents of Jacob the man who does this,
        the one who is awake and who answers, and the one who brings an offering
        to Yahweh of hosts! '
      comments: []
    - name: '13: '
      title: 
      number: 13
      content: 'And this you do as well: you cover the altar of Yahweh with tears,
        with weeping and with groaning, because he no longer regards the offering
        or accepts it with favor from your hand. '
      comments: []
    - name: '14: '
      title: 
      number: 14
      content: "But you ask, \u201CFor what reason?\u201D Because Yahweh stands as
        a witness between you and the wife of your youth, against whom you have been
        unfaithful, even though she is your marriage partner and your wife by covenant.  "
      comments: []
    - name: '15: '
      title: 
      number: 15
      content: 'Did not one God make them? But a remnant of the spirit is his. And
        what does the one God desire? An offspring of God. You must be attentive
        to your spirit, and you must not be unfaithful to the wife of your youth. '
      comments: []
    - name: '16: '
      title: 
      number: 16
      content: "\u201CFor I hate divorce,\u201D says Yahweh, the God of Israel, \u201Cand
        he who covers his clothing with violence,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. \u201CYou
        must be attentive to your spirit and you must not be unfaithful.\u201D "
      comments: []
    - name: '17: '
      title: 
      number: 17
      content: "You have wearied Yahweh with your words, but you ask, \u201CWith
        what have we wearied him?\u201D You have done so when you say, \u201CEveryone
        who does evil is good in the sight of Yahweh, and in them he delights,\u201D
        or \u201CWhere is the God of justice?\u201D "
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - name: "1: Yahweh\u2019s Messenger is Coming"
      title: "Yahweh\u2019s Messenger is Coming"
      number: 1
      content: "\u201CLook! I am going to send my messenger, and he will prepare
        the way before me. And the Lord whom you are seeking will come suddenly to
        his temple, and the messenger of the covenant, in whom you are taking pleasure\u2014look!\u2014he
        is about to come,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '2: '
      title: 
      number: 2
      content: "And who can endure the day of his coming? And who is the one who
        can stand when he appears? For he is like a refiner\u2019s fire, like launderers\u2019
        alkali.  "
      comments: []
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: 'He will sit as a refiner and purifier of silver; he will purify the
        children of Levi, and he will refine them like gold and like silver, and
        they will present to Yahweh offerings in righteousness. '
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: 'And the offering of Judah and Jerusalem will be pleasing to Yahweh,
        like in the days of old and like in former years. '
      comments: []
    - name: '5: An Overflowing Blessing'
      title: An Overflowing Blessing
      number: 5
      content: "\u201CThen I will approach you for judgment, and I will be a swift
        witness against the sorcerers and against the adulterers, and against those
        who swear falsely, and against the oppressors of the hired worker with his
        wages, the widow and the orphan, and the abusers of the alien, and yet do
        not fear me,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: "\u201CFor I, Yahweh, have not changed, and you, O children of Jacob,
        have not perished.  "
      comments: []
    - name: '7: '
      title: 
      number: 7
      content: "From the days of your ancestors you have turned aside from my rules,
        and have not kept them! Return to me and I will return to you,\u201D says
        Yahweh of hosts, \u201Cbut you say, \u2018How shall we return?\u2019 "
      comments: []
    - name: '8: '
      title: 
      number: 8
      content: "Will a human dare to rob God? Yet you are robbing me! And you say,
        \u2018How have we robbed you?\u2019 In the tithes and the contributions! "
      comments: []
    - name: '9: '
      title: 
      number: 9
      content: 'You are being cursed with a curse, for you are robbing me, the whole
        nation of you! '
      comments: []
    - name: '10: '
      title: 
      number: 10
      content: "Bring the whole tithe to the storehouse, so that there will be food
        in my house, and test me please in this,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts, \u201Cif
        I will not open for you the windows of heaven, and pour forth for you an
        overflowing blessing.  "
      comments: []
    - name: '11: '
      title: 
      number: 11
      content: "I will rebuke the devourer for you; it will not destroy the fruit
        of your soil; your vine in the field will not be unfruitful,\u201D says Yahweh
        of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '12: '
      title: 
      number: 12
      content: "\u201CAnd all the nations will call you blessed, because you will
        be a land in which one takes joy,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '13: '
      title: 
      number: 13
      content: "\u201CYour words have been harsh against me,\u201D says Yahweh. \u201CBut
        you say, \u2018How have we spoken together against you?\u2019 "
      comments: []
    - name: '14: '
      title: 
      number: 14
      content: "You have said, \u2018It is useless to serve God! What is the gain
        if we keep his requirements, and if we walk as mourners before Yahweh of
        hosts? "
      comments: []
    - name: '15: A Book of Remembrance is Written'
      title: A Book of Remembrance is Written
      number: 15
      content: "And now we are calling the arrogant blessed! Not only do those who
        do wickedness prosper; they also test God and they escape!\u2019&nbsp;\u201D "
      comments: []
    - name: '16: '
      title: 
      number: 16
      content: 'Then those who revered Yahweh spoke with one another. And Yahweh
        listened attentively and heard, and a scroll of remembrance was written before
        him of those who revere Yahweh and ponder his name. '
      comments: []
    - name: '17: '
      title: 
      number: 17
      content: "\u201CThey will be mine,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts, \u201Con the
        day that I am acting, my treasured possession. I will have compassion on
        them as a man has compassion on his son who serves him. "
      comments: []
    - name: '18: '
      title: 
      number: 18
      content: 'You will return and see the difference between the righteous and
        the wicked, between the one who serves God and the one who does not serve
        him. '
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - name: '1: '
      title: 
      number: 1
      content: "   \u201CFor look! The day is about to come, burning like an oven,
        and all the arrogant and every evildoer will be stubble. The coming day will
        consume them,\u201D says Yahweh of hosts. \u201CIt will not leave behind
        for them root or branch. "
      comments: []
    - name: '2: '
      title: 
      number: 2
      content: 'But for you who revere my name, the sun of righteousness will rise,
        with healing in its wings, and you will go out and leap like fattened calves.  '
      comments: []
    - name: '3: '
      title: 
      number: 3
      content: "You will trample down the wicked, for they will be ashes under the
        soles of your feet on the day that I am going to act,\u201D says Yahweh of
        hosts. "
      comments: []
    - name: '4: '
      title: 
      number: 4
      content: "\u201CRemember the instruction of my servant Moses, which I commanded
        him at Horeb to all Israel, the rules and regulations. "
      comments: []
    - name: '5: '
      title: 
      number: 5
      content: 'Look! I am going to send to you Elijah the prophet before the coming
        of the great and awesome day of Yahweh! '
      comments: []
    - name: '6: '
      title: 
      number: 6
      content: "And he will bring back the hearts of the fathers to the sons, and
        the hearts of the sons to their fathers, so that I will not come and strike
        the land with a ban.\u201D "
      comments: []
